        "subject": "LU-4398 tests: re-enable sanity test 817",
        "message": "LU-4398 tests: re-enable sanity test 817\n\nIt was reported in the LU-4398 jira ticket that ARM had general\nissues with reporting ETXTBSY for file access. This was true in\ngeneral for even NFS. Re-enable the test to see if new kernels\nfor ARM have addressed this issue.\n\nChange-Id: If9054e40a37355d381608f3cf6d7b4d21b1b8f0d\nTest-Parameters: trivial clientarch=aarch64\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
